Invocation Name: plan my day
des: This application will suggest a new work or thing to do on that day and some random facts too. This is so useful when you feel bored or don't know how to spend your day .This application will take off your boredom and fill it with joy. You will love it .
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
